Ontario Regulator Says It’s Reviewing Firms Operating in Emerging Markets

-- B y   D a v i d   S c a n l a n
-- 
2011-07-05T20:42:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-05/ontario-regulator-says-it-s-reviewing-firms-operating-in-emerging-markets.html
 The Ontario Securities Commission
said today it has begun a “targeted review” of Ontario
companies listed on Canadian exchanges that have
“significant business operations in emerging markets.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  